data.description:
This spacious home has a fantastic location. 
You will love that the primary bedroom has a spacious loft and private balcony that overlooks the franklin mountains. Downstairs you will find an additional 3 bedrooms, one of which is a junior suite with a private bath.  The home has a formal dining and living rooms and lots of space outdoors to entertain. It offers impressive features such as a fireplace, plantation shutters, hardwood & tile floors, and stainless steel appliances. The kitchen has plenty of cabinetry and counter top space! Beautiful front & back landscaping, covered patio and outdoor storage shed. Call today to see it!
